    <content>
      <![CDATA[<blockquote><p>这是我做 OpenCloud Agent 时踩的最有意思的一个坑：Ollama 给你的流式输出是一堆逐 token 的碎片，你得自己拼回来，还得同时拆出三样东西——正文、思维链、JSON 命令。这篇文章记录我是怎么搞定的。</p></blockquote><h2 id="问题：Ollama-给了你什么"><a href="#问题：Ollama-给了你什么" class="headerlink" title="问题：Ollama 给了你什么"></a>问题：Ollama 给了你什么</h2><p>Ollama 的 <code>/api/chat</code> 接口开启 <code>stream: true</code> 后，返回的是 SSE 格式的逐行 JSON：</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Plaintext"><figure class="iseeu highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;&quot;model&quot;:&quot;qwen3&quot;,&quot;message&quot;:&#123;&quot;content&quot;:&quot;用&quot;&#125;,&quot;done&quot;:false&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;&quot;model&quot;:&quot;qwen3&quot;,&quot;message&quot;:&#123;&quot;content&quot;:&quot;户&quot;&#125;,&quot;done&quot;:false&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;&quot;model&quot;:&quot;qwen3&quot;,&quot;message&quot;:&#123;&quot;content&quot;:&quot;好&quot;&#125;,&quot;done&quot;:false&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;&quot;model&quot;:&quot;qwen3&quot;,&quot;message&quot;:&#123;&quot;content&quot;:&quot;&lt;think&gt;&quot;&#125;,&quot;done&quot;:false&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;&quot;model&quot;:&quot;qwen3&quot;,&quot;message&quot;:&#123;&quot;content&quot;:&quot;这&quot;&#125;,&quot;done&quot;:false&#125;</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">&#123;&quot;model&quot;:&quot;qwen3&quot;,&quot;message&quot;:&#123;&quot;content&quot;:&quot;&lt;/think&gt;&quot;&#125;,&quot;done&quot;:false&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;&quot;model&quot;:&quot;qwen3&quot;,&quot;message&quot;:&#123;&quot;content&quot;:&quot;\n&quot;&#125;,&quot;done&quot;:false&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;&quot;model&quot;:&quot;qwen3&quot;,&quot;message&quot;:&#123;&quot;content&quot;:&quot;&#123;&quot;&#125;,&quot;done&quot;:false&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;&quot;model&quot;:&quot;qwen3&quot;,&quot;message&quot;:&#123;&quot;content&quot;:&quot;\&quot;command\&quot;&quot;&#125;,&quot;done&quot;:false&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;&quot;model&quot;:&quot;qwen3&quot;,&quot;message&quot;:&#123;&quot;content&quot;:&quot;:&quot;&#125;,&quot;done&quot;:false&#125;</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>一个字一个字蹦。而且——<strong>Ollama SDK 不帮你做任何解析</strong>。<code>&lt;think&gt;</code> 标签？你自己拆。JSON 命令块？你自己检测。JSON 跨 chunk？你自己拼。</p><p>我需要从这堆碎片里分离出三个通道：</p><table><thead><tr><th>通道</th><th>用途</th><th>来源</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>text</code></td><td>给用户看的正文</td><td>模型输出的普通文本</td></tr><tr><td><code>thinking</code></td><td>思维链，CLI 里单独渲染</td><td><code>&lt;think&gt;...&lt;/think&gt;</code> 内的内容</td></tr><tr><td><code>command</code></td><td>工具调用命令</td><td><code>{ &quot;command&quot;: &quot;...&quot;, &quot;params&quot;: {...} }</code></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="第一关：拆-标签"><a href="#第一关：拆-标签" class="headerlink" title="第一关：拆 &lt;think&gt; 标签"></a>第一关：拆 <code>&lt;think&gt;</code> 标签</h2><h3 id="朴素想法"><a href="#朴素想法" class="headerlink" title="朴素想法"></a>朴素想法</h3><p>正则一把梭：<code>re.findall(r&#39;&lt;think&gt;(.*?)&lt;/think&gt;&#39;, full_text)</code>。</p><p><strong>问题</strong>：这是流式输出。你不能等全部文本到齐再拆——那跟非流式有什么区别？用户要的是逐字打字效果。</p><p>而且 <code>&lt;think&gt;</code> 标签的开闭可能被切到不同的 chunk 里：</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Plaintext"><figure class="iseeu highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chunk 23: &quot;我在想&lt;th&quot;</span><br><span class="line">chunk 24: &quot;ink&gt;这个问题&quot;</span><br><span class="line">chunk 25: &quot;应该&lt;/thi&quot;</span><br><span class="line">chunk 26: &quot;nk&gt;这样解决&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>正则在半个标签上根本匹配不到。</p><h3 id="我的解法：状态机-末尾保留"><a href="#我的解法：状态机-末尾保留" class="headerlink" title="我的解法：状态机 + 末尾保留"></a>我的解法：状态机 + 末尾保留</h3><p>核心思路是一个简单的状态机，两个状态：<code>in_thinking = True/False</code>。关键 trick 是：<strong>每次输出时检查末尾是否有未完成的标签前缀，如果有就留在 buffer 里不输出。</strong></p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Python"><figure class="iseeu highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">in_thinking = <span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line">buffer = <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">for</span> line <span class="keyword">in</span> resp.aiter_lines():</span><br><span class="line">    chunk = json.loads(line)</span><br><span class="line">    token = chunk.get(<span class="string">&quot;message&quot;</span>, &#123;&#125;).get(<span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    buffer += token</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> buffer:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> in_thinking:</span><br><span class="line">            open_idx = buffer.find(<span class="string">&quot;&lt;think&gt;&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> open_idx == -<span class="number">1</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment"># 没有开标签，但末尾可能有未完成的 &quot;&lt;th&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="string">&quot;&lt;th&quot;</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> buffer:</span><br><span class="line">                    idx = buffer.rfind(<span class="string">&quot;&lt;th&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">yield</span> &#123;<span class="string">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>: buffer[:idx]&#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    buffer = buffer[idx:]  <span class="comment"># 保留未完成部分</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">yield</span> &#123;<span class="string">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>: buffer&#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    buffer = <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment"># 输出开标签前的文本，进入思维链模式</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> open_idx &gt; <span class="number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">yield</span> &#123;<span class="string">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>: buffer[:open_idx]&#125;</span><br><span class="line">                buffer = buffer[open_idx + <span class="number">7</span>:]  <span class="comment"># 跳过 &quot;&lt;think&gt;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">                in_thinking = <span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            close_idx = buffer.find(<span class="string">&quot;&lt;/think&gt;&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> close_idx == -<span class="number">1</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment"># 还在思维链中，但末尾可能有未完成的 &quot;&lt;/&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="string">&quot;&lt;/&quot;</span> <span class="keyword">in</span> buffer:</span><br><span class="line">                    idx = buffer.rfind(<span class="string">&quot;&lt;/&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">yield</span> &#123;<span class="string">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;thinking&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>: buffer[:idx]&#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    buffer = buffer[idx:]</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">yield</span> &#123;<span class="string">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;thinking&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>: buffer&#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    buffer = <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment"># 思维链结束</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">yield</span> &#123;<span class="string">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;thinking&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>: buffer[:close_idx]&#125;</span><br><span class="line">                buffer = buffer[close_idx + <span class="number">8</span>:]  <span class="comment"># 跳过 &quot;&lt;/think&gt;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">                in_thinking = <span class="literal">False</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><strong>关键点</strong>：<code>rfind(&quot;&lt;th&quot;)</code> 和 <code>rfind(&quot;&lt;/&quot;)</code> 这两个”末尾保留”逻辑。它们确保即使标签被切断，碎片留在 buffer 里等下一个 chunk 拼完整。</p><p>这个 pattern 后来我在很多流式处理场景中都用了——不只是标签，任何”标记可能跨 chunk”的场景都适用。</p><h2 id="第二关：JSON-命令块检测"><a href="#第二关：JSON-命令块检测" class="headerlink" title="第二关：JSON 命令块检测"></a>第二关：JSON 命令块检测</h2><p>模型不只输出文字，还会输出工具调用命令：</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Json"><figure class="iseeu highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;command&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;web_search&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span> <span class="attr">&quot;params&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;query&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;Ollama streaming&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>这个命令块需要被检测、提取、解析成结构化数据传给工具执行器。</p><h3 id="朴素想法-1"><a href="#朴素想法-1" class="headerlink" title="朴素想法"></a>朴素想法</h3><p>按行分割，找 <code>{</code> 开头的行，<code>json.loads</code> 解析。</p><p><strong>问题</strong>：命令块经常跨 chunk。上面那个 JSON 可能是这样来的：</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Plaintext"><figure class="iseeu highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chunk 31: &#x27;&#123;&quot;comma&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">chunk 32: &#x27;nd&quot;: &quot;we&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">chunk 33: &#x27;b_search&quot;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">chunk 34: &#x27;, &quot;par&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">chunk 35: &#x27;ams&quot;: &#123;&quot;q&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">chunk 36: &#x27;uery&quot;: &quot;Ol&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">chunk 37: &#x27;lama strea&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">chunk 38: &#x27;ming&quot;&#125;&#125;&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>按行分？根本没换行。按 chunk 分？一个 chunk 不是一个完整 JSON。</p><h3 id="我的解法：花括号深度计数-缓冲区"><a href="#我的解法：花括号深度计数-缓冲区" class="headerlink" title="我的解法：花括号深度计数 + 缓冲区"></a>我的解法：花括号深度计数 + 缓冲区</h3><p>思路：一旦检测到 JSON 命令块的起始标记 <code>{&quot;command&quot;</code>，就进入”JSON 模式”，把后续所有 token 攒进 buffer，用花括号深度计数判断什么时候 JSON 完整了。</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Python"><figure class="iseeu highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">StreamParser</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    JSON_START = re.<span class="built_in">compile</span>(<span class="string">r&#x27;\&#123;\s*&quot;command&quot;\s*:&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.buffer = <span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">self</span>.in_json = <span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">_process_buffer</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> <span class="variable language_">self</span>.buffer:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="variable language_">self</span>.in_json:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment"># 寻找 JSON 开始位置</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">match</span> = <span class="variable language_">self</span>.JSON_START.search(<span class="variable language_">self</span>.buffer)</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="keyword">match</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="comment"># 没有 JSON，输出安全部分（保留末尾可能的 &quot;&#123;&quot;）</span></span><br><span class="line">                    ...</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="comment"># 输出 JSON 前的文本</span></span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="keyword">match</span>.start() &gt; <span class="number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                        <span class="keyword">yield</span> &#123;<span class="string">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>: <span class="variable language_">self</span>.buffer[:<span class="keyword">match</span>.start()]&#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="variable language_">self</span>.buffer = <span class="variable language_">self</span>.buffer[<span class="keyword">match</span>.start():]</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="variable language_">self</span>.in_json = <span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment"># 在 JSON 块中，尝试提取完整 JSON</span></span><br><span class="line">                cmd = <span class="variable language_">self</span>._try_extract_json()</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> cmd:</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">yield</span> &#123;<span class="string">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;command&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;data&quot;</span>: cmd&#125;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="variable language_">self</span>.in_json = <span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">break</span>  <span class="comment"># JSON 不完整，等更多数据</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>核心是 <code>_try_extract_json()</code>——逐字符扫描，跟踪花括号深度：</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Python"><figure class="iseeu highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">_try_extract_json</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    depth = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">    in_string = <span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line">    escape = <span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i, ch <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">enumerate</span>(<span class="variable language_">self</span>.buffer):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> escape:</span><br><span class="line">            escape = <span class="literal">False</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">continue</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> ch == <span class="string">&quot;\\&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            escape = <span class="literal">True</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">continue</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> ch == <span class="string">&#x27;&quot;&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            in_string = <span class="keyword">not</span> in_string</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">continue</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> in_string:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">continue</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> ch == <span class="string">&quot;&#123;&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            depth += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">elif</span> ch == <span class="string">&quot;&#125;&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            depth -= <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> depth == <span class="number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment"># 花括号配平了，JSON 完整</span></span><br><span class="line">                json_str = <span class="variable language_">self</span>.buffer[:i + <span class="number">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line">                cmd = <span class="variable language_">self</span>._try_parse_json(json_str)</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span> cmd:</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="variable language_">self</span>.buffer = <span class="variable language_">self</span>.buffer[i + <span class="number">1</span>:]</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="keyword">return</span> cmd</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">None</span>  <span class="comment"># 还没配平，等更多数据</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><strong>三个要注意的点：</strong></p><ol><li><strong>字符串内的花括号不算</strong>。<code>&quot;params&quot;: {&quot;query&quot;: &quot;{test}&quot;}</code> 里的 <code>{test}</code> 不能影响深度计数。所以要跟踪 <code>in_string</code> 状态。</li><li><strong>转义字符</strong>。<code>&quot;path&quot;: &quot;C:\\folder&quot;</code> 里的 <code>\\</code> 后面的引号不能翻转 <code>in_string</code>。所以要有 <code>escape</code> 标志。</li><li><strong>markdown 包裹</strong>。模型有时会把 JSON 包在 <code>```json ... ```</code> 里，解析前要剥掉。</li></ol><h2 id="第三关：两个解析器怎么串起来"><a href="#第三关：两个解析器怎么串起来" class="headerlink" title="第三关：两个解析器怎么串起来"></a>第三关：两个解析器怎么串起来</h2><p><code>&lt;think&gt;</code> 拆分和 JSON 检测不能在同一步做——因为思维链里可能包含看起来像 JSON 的文本（模型在思考时可能写示例）。</p><p>我的架构是分两层：</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Plaintext"><figure class="iseeu highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Ollama SSE</span><br><span class="line">    │</span><br><span class="line">    ▼</span><br><span class="line">┌──────────┐</span><br><span class="line">│ model.py │  拆 &lt;think&gt; 标签</span><br><span class="line">│          │  → text 事件 / thinking 事件 / done 事件</span><br><span class="line">└────┬─────┘</span><br><span class="line">     │</span><br><span class="line">     ▼</span><br><span class="line">┌──────────┐</span><br><span class="line">│parser.py │  从 text 事件中检测 JSON 命令块</span><br><span class="line">│          │  → text 事件 / command 事件 / done 事件</span><br><span class="line">└──────────┘</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>model.py 先把流拆成 <code>text</code> 和 <code>thinking</code> 事件。parser.py 只处理 <code>text</code> 事件中的 JSON 命令块，<code>thinking</code> 事件直接透传。</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Python"><figure class="iseeu highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">feed</span>(<span class="params">self, events</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">for</span> event <span class="keyword">in</span> events:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> event[<span class="string">&quot;type&quot;</span>] == <span class="string">&quot;thinking&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">yield</span> event  <span class="comment"># 思维链不参与 JSON 检测，直接透传</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">continue</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> event[<span class="string">&quot;type&quot;</span>] == <span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="variable language_">self</span>.buffer += event[<span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>]</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">async</span> <span class="keyword">for</span> evt <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="variable language_">self</span>._process_buffer():</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">yield</span> evt</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">elif</span> event[<span class="string">&quot;type&quot;</span>] == <span class="string">&quot;done&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment"># 冲刷缓冲区</span></span><br><span class="line">            ...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p>这样思维链里的假 JSON 不会被误判为命令。</p><h2 id="一个容易忽略的边界情况"><a href="#一个容易忽略的边界情况" class="headerlink" title="一个容易忽略的边界情况"></a>一个容易忽略的边界情况</h2><p>模型输出 JSON 命令块之前，可能先输出一些正文文本。比如：</p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Plaintext"><figure class="iseeu highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">好的，我来帮你搜索一下。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#123;&quot;command&quot;: &quot;web_search&quot;, &quot;params&quot;: &#123;&quot;query&quot;: &quot;...&quot;&#125;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><code>&quot;好的，我来帮你搜索一下。\n\n&quot;</code> 这部分要作为 <code>text</code> 事件输出给用户，不能被吞掉。</p><p>但反过来，如果 buffer 末尾只有一个 <code>{</code>，它可能是 JSON 命令的开始，也可能是正文里的一个花括号。我的处理方式是：<strong>保留末尾最多 20 个字符中最后一个 <code>{</code> 之后的 内容</strong>，等下一个 chunk 来了再判断。如果后面跟着 <code>&quot;command&quot;</code>，进入 JSON 模式；如果没有，就当普通文本输出。</p><p>这个”等一等”的策略会让正文末尾有最多 20 字符的延迟，但对用户体验影响很小。</p><h2 id="效果"><a href="#效果" class="headerlink" title="效果"></a>效果</h2><p>最终的 CLI 渲染效果：</p><ul><li>正文实时逐字打出</li><li>思维链在单独的面板里展示，灰色斜体</li><li>命令块触发工具执行面板，显示工具名和参数</li></ul><p>三通道并行，互不干扰。用户看到的是一个流畅的对话界面，背后是两个解析器在逐 token 地拆分流式数据。</p><h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><table><thead><tr><th>问题</th><th>朴素方案</th><th>为什么不行</th><th>我的方案</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>&lt;think&gt;</code> 跨 chunk</td><td>正则匹配</td><td>半个标签匹配不到</td><td>状态机 + 末尾保留</td></tr><tr><td>JSON 跨 chunk</td><td>按行分割</td><td>命令块没有换行</td><td>花括号深度计数 + 缓冲区</td></tr><tr><td>思维链内的假 JSON</td><td>一起检测</td><td>误触发命令</td><td>分层解析，thinking 透传</td></tr></tbody></table><p>核心教训就一句：<strong>流式数据不能等齐了再处理，但也不能盲目地按 chunk 处理。你需要一个缓冲区 + 一个状态机，让数据”流”过你的解析逻辑，在每个 token 到来时做增量判断。</strong></p><p>这套东西写完之后，我发现它其实是一个很通用的 pattern。任何”结构化数据混在非结构化流里”的场景都能用：日志解析、协议拆包、混合内容渲染。AI Agent 只是触发我去想这个问题的契机。</p>]]>
    </content>
